&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Job Description&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;CSCI Consulting is seeking an experienced &lt;strong&gt;Agile Scrum Master&lt;/strong&gt; to support a federal government client in delivering mission-critical technology solutions using Agile and Scaled Agile Framework (SAFe) methodologies. The Scrum Master will serve as a servant leader, Agile coach, and facilitator, helping teams deliver high-quality solutions while fostering continuous improvement and collaboration across stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Lead and coach Agile teams operating within a Scaled Agile Framework (SAFe)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Facilitate Program Increment (PI) Planning, sprint planning, retrospectives, demos, and other Agile ceremonies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Guide teams in developing PI objectives and aligning work to program priorities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Partner with Product Owners and Business Analysts to support backlog refinement and prioritization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Identify, track, and remove impediments while coordinating with stakeholders to resolve dependencies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Monitor team performance using Agile metrics and drive continuous process improvements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Collaborate with other Scrum Masters to ensure consistency of Agile practices across teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Coordinate with architects, cybersecurity teams, developers, and business stakeholders to support successful delivery&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Support release planning and management of cross-team dependencies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Mentor and coach team members to develop high-performing, self-organizing teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Assist with capacity planning, resource allocation, and staffing coordination&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Ensure quality, timeliness, and successful execution of assigned work&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Minimum Requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Active Secret security clearance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Job Description&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;CSCI Consulting is seeking an accomplished COBOL Developer to join our dynamic team. The ideal candidate will possess extensive experience in COBOL programming and a robust understanding of mainframe systems. In this role, you will be instrumental in developing, maintaining, and supporting COBOL applications, ensuring they meet the highest standards and effectively serve our clients&#39; needs. This is an exciting opportunity to leverage your expertise in a collaborative and innovative environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Design, code, test, and debug COBOL programs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Maintain and enhance existing COBOL applications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to gather requirements and provide technical solution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Perform system analysis and troubleshooting to resolve issues&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Ensure code quality and adherence to best practices&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Document technical specifications and processes&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Minimum Requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;5+ years of experience in COBOL development within a mainframe environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Strong understanding of mainframe systems and COBOL programming&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Experience with one or more of the following a plus: &amp;nbsp;ADS-Online, ADS-Batch, CICS, Job Control Language, MQ Series, Structured Query Language (SQL)&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Job Description&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Ready to take your Mainframe IDMS and COBOL skills to the next level? CSCI Consulting is on the hunt for a Senior Developer with at least 5 years of experience to support a &lt;strong&gt;cutting-edge federal project&lt;/strong&gt;. If you’re looking for a role that’s as challenging as it is rewarding, we want you on our team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Conducts multidisciplinary research and collaborates with equipment designers and/or hardware engineers in the planning, design, development, and utilization of electronic data processing systems for product and commercial software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Determines computer user needs; analyzes system capabilities to resolve problems on program intent, output requirements, input data acquisition, programming techniques and controls; prepares operating instructions; designs and develops compilers and assemblers, utility programs, and operating systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Ensures software standards are met. Analyzes user needs and software requirements to determine feasibility of design within time and cost constraints&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Confers with systems analysts, engineers, programmers and others to design system and to obtain information on project limitations and capabilities, performance requirements and interfaces&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Designs, develops and modifies software systems, using scientific analysis and mathematical models to predict and measure outcomes and consequences of design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Coordinates software system installations and monitors equipment functioning to ensure specifications are met&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Modify existing databases and database management systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Write and code logical and physical database descriptions and specify identifiers of database to management system or direct others in coding descriptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Work as part of a project team to coordinate database development and determine project scope and limitations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Review project requests describing database user needs to estimate time and cost required to accomplish project&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Minimum Requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in computer science, software engineering or relevant field required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;5 years’ experience in Mainframe IDMS and COBOL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Creativity and adaptability in problem-solving&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Ability to work with clients to understand their needs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Strong organizational and time-management skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45,

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Job Description&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;CSCI Consulting is seeking a highly driven FIAR Analyst to support our elite Department of War client. In this critical role, you will play a key part in strengthening audit readiness efforts, enhancing internal controls, and contributing to mission success at the highest levels of national defense. This is an excellent opportunity to work alongside senior stakeholders and auditors in a fast-paced, high-impact environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Prepare and update business process maps, narratives, and process cycle memorandums to support audit readiness initiatives&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Evaluate internal controls and provide recommendations to improve design effectiveness and operational efficiency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Partner with internal and external auditors to support audit activities and ensure timely resolution of findings&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Collaborate with command stakeholders to identify process gaps and implement sustainable improvements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Develop detailed test plans and perform control testing to assess compliance with FIAR requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Analyze financial and operational processes to ensure alignment with DoW financial management standards&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Minimum Requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Eligibility to obtain a Top Secret clearance with SCI eligibility&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;1–2 years of Special Operations Forces (SOF) experience in a joint environment, with exposure to one or more of the following:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;FIAR budgetary and accounting support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;FIAR logistics support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;FIAR system Complementary User Entity Control (CUEC) support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;Demonstrated problem-solving skills with the ability to think creatively and adapt in dynamic environments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 45, 64);&quot;&gt;&lt;span

&lt;p&gt;At CSCI Consulting, we’re always looking for talented, driven individuals who share our commitment to superior service and innovative solutions. Don’t see the right role today? Submit a &lt;strong&gt;general application&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to stay on our radar for future opportunities!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re passionate about solving challenges, delivering results, and making an impact, we want to hear from you. At CSCI, our people are our greatest asset—and you could be the perfect fit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We look forward to connecting with you!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: montserrat light, arial, sans-serif; color: #00aae7;&quot; data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;About CSCI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: merriweather, georgia, serif; color: #002d40;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;CSCI is an award-winning information technology and financial management consulting firm founded on one simple philosophy: “Do what is right, always.” We apply this philosophy across all elements of our growing business, from delivering world-class s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;ervices for customers to providing an environment where associates thrive both personally and professionally. At CSCI, work and fun aren’t diametrically opposed!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: merriweather, georgia, serif; color: #002d40;&quot; data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;At CSCI, our goal is to hire people with proven track records and retain them with an energizing, diverse company culture. We value each associate’s natural drive to excel, and we provide them with the freedom to do things their way. CSCI seeks the best and brightest in the industry—those who are ready to move their lives and career forward. Join us today and get excited about Mondays again!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: merriweather, arial, sans-serif; color: #002d40;&quot; data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Benefits of Working at CSCI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: merriweather, georgia, serif; color: #002d40;&quot; data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;40&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233528&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335551500&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: merriweather, georgia, serif; color: #002d40;&quot; data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Competitive salaries&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: merriweather, georgia, serif; color: #002d40;&quot; data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;40&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233528&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335551500&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: merriweather, georgia, serif; color: #002d40;&quot; data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Generous Paid Time Off (PTO) package&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: merriweather, georgia, se

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Job Description&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;CSCI Consulting is looking for &lt;/span&gt;a skilled Information System Security Engineer (ISSE) to support a Department of Defense (DoD) modernization initiative. This role provides the opportunity to apply hands-on cybersecurity engineering expertise across complex on-premises and cloud environments while supporting mission-critical transportation and logistics operations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;As part of a collaborative cybersecurity team, you will work alongside architects, ISSOs, system administrators, and government stakeholders to implement security controls, strengthen system security posture, and support compliance with Department of Defense cybersecurity requirements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Implement and document Security Technical Implementation Guide (STIG) configurations across assigned systems and platforms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Conduct Security Impact Analyses (SIAs) for system modifications, upgrades, and enhancements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Execute automated compliance validation and configuration assessments using SCAP Compliance Checker&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Manage vulnerability identification, tracking, remediation, and reporting activities using Tenable Security Center or similar tools&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Assess cloud infrastructure security posture utilizing Tenable Cloud Security or comparable cloud security assessment platforms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Support CyberArk Privileged Access Management (PAM) implementation and administration activities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain secure configuration baselines and system hardening standards&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Author technical security implementation guides and supporting cybersecurity documentation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Collaborate with engineering and cybersecurity teams to implement and validate security controls&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Support cybersecurity architecture initiatives and technical security implementations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;Minimum Requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot; data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(52, 73, 94);&quot;&gt;Active Secret Security Clearance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
